  "texts": [
    "See the NeurIPS code and data submission guidelines (https: //nips.cc/public/guides/CodeSubmissionPolicy) for more details.",
    "• The authors should provide instructions on data access and preparation, including how to access the raw data, preprocessed data, intermediate data, and generated data, etc.",
    "• The authors should provide scripts to reproduce all experimental results for the new proposed method and baselines.",
    "If only a subset of experiments are reproducible, they should state which ones are omitted from the script and why.",
    "• At submission time, to preserve anonymity, the authors should release anonymized versions (if applicable)."
  ],
